    java.io.Serializable

    public class DeepstreamLoginException
extends java.lang.Exception
    A DeepstreamLoginException occurs if you login to a connection that was forcefully closed due to Event.UNAUTHENTICATED_CONNECTION_TIMEOUT or if the login attempts exceed the maximum Event.TOO_MANY_AUTH_ATTEMPTS
